<lyrics>[V1]
 O! fiderana, fiderana Anao Andriamanitra ô!
 O! fiderana, fiderana Anao Andriamanitra ô!
 Fihobiana ,fihobiana Anao Andriamanitra ô!
 Fiderana, fiderana fankalazana
 Fihobiana ny Anaranao
 No hirainay ety an-tany
 No hiraina any an-danitra any
 Haleloia, haleloia, haleloia
 Haleloia, haleloia
 No hirainay ety an-tany
 No hiraina any an-danitra any
 O! fiderana, fiderana Anao Andriamanitra ô!
 O! fiderana, fiderana Anao Andriamanitra ô!</lyrics>
